    "Additionally, a non-exhaustive exploration was conducted using the Google search engine without the search string previously mentioned, due to its capacity to offer a broader range of information than traditional academic search engines.",
    "The PRISMA methodology (Page et al. 2021) was used for the systematic search described in phases one and two.",
    "For their respective selection (on literature and tools), the eligibility criteria shown in Table 4 were applied.",
    "The literature and tools selection flow is shown in Figs.",
    "3 and 4, respectively."
